{"tid":390533,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"個個都想拍拖唔通個個都想拍拖咩","createTime":"2017-09-07T07:01:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-07T07:54:22.000Z","uid":9941,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3ca778b22dcd00285862df6143e94051c7d1eb86","tid":390533,"uid":9941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T07:01:25.000Z","msg":"呢句其實真係好哲學<br />\n之前同fd傾開計佢都話無諗過同現任結婚<br />\n唔分手只係無切入點<br />\n理想中既拍拖係大家真心相愛<br />\n但係現實又有幾多對係<br />\n更多既只係一方有愛<br />\n而另一方只係唔抗拒<br />\n又唔想咁dry就拍住先<br />\n亦即係散拖<br />\n世人都係睇得太多電影<br />\n再睇睇離婚數字<br />\n又望望幾多偽人婚事<br />\n如果真係搵到真心相愛其實真係幾生修到<br />\n因為拍緊拖都唔等於相愛<br />\n情人節一對對拖住既手<br />\n都可能只係一對又一對冷冰冰既手<br />\n而身為一個毒撚都係繼續搵三上算<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n叫完春<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c022c81f8313321a7a5a9cbbb0f9f03c62145c97","tid":390533,"uid":9941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T07:07:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f682fd9d4cf0ce3aee24814976ac58db0d517ef8","tid":390533,"uid":9941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T07:07:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf4607dd3f31467d3e0f174127bc027e896e1151","tid":390533,"uid":9941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T07:08:27.000Z","msg":"負評可唔可以講下點解"},{"pid":"301e058984f0214d35194c5b799ebad6b2e75838","tid":390533,"uid":32584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T07:09:01.000Z","msg":"所以其實一直都覺得句野無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9673e46e44a626ae0fd7154110965b9608c69986","tid":390533,"uid":62842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T07:12:54.000Z","msg":"Agger"},{"pid":"4cbced70112681c92f2313d3aa9be20d6